hopobject.body: How much is a First Class stamp? powermax treadmill review india However, the president's climate change initiatives do not involve any sort of compromise. During the last presidential campaign, Obama backed off from criticizing the coal industry and even mentioned coal as part of the comprehensive energy solution. His strategy was to gain favor in battleground states such as Virginia and Pennsylvania. Now he has no need for the coal companies and their workers and is doing everything in his power to obliterate the industry by choosing winners and losers instead of letting the free market decide.
